{"about_the_game":"\u25c6This board game is a mahjong game played by 4 people or computer.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119440/extras/steam_001.png?t=1718778877\" /><br>You can play with 3 ai users by yourself, Or you can play Mahjong with 3 other real users.<br><br>\u25c6This game supports traditional [Chinese mahjong] and [Japanese riich mahjong].<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119440/extras/steam_002.png?t=1718778877\" /><br>Tutorials, practice( single play mode ), and online play ( 4 user play mode ) supported.<br>We provide two styles of mahjong tiles for western players unfamiliar with mahjong games.<br><br>\u25c6You can learn how to play Mahjong by investing only 10 minutes in the tutorial.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119440/extras/steam_003.png?t=1718778877\" /><br><br>This game requires a network connection for online play. If the network connection is not smooth, the game will not play normally.<br>The game also supports single play game with AI players.<br><br>\u25c6Mahjong is a game that requires skill.<br>Our games are played by thousands of real users every day.<br>More than 30% of users have played this game more than 10,000 times.<br>You'll have to play that much and you'll be of average skill.<br>If you are in doubt about the game opponent, please report it using the replay function.<br><br>\u25c6This game has in-app purchase items.<br>You can purchase 3, 5, 9, 30, or 50 gold items.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119440/extras/steam_005.png?t=1718778877\" /><br>Purchased gold can be used to exchange for game money, avatars, and other items.<br><br>Many Mahjong players await your challenge.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119440